<LP>
   TEXTRON Inc. (Providence, R.I.) -- Russell G. Downing, 44
years old, was named president of the Randall division of
this aerospace, financial services and commercial products
concern, succeeding Richard J. Price, 64, who was named to
the new position of chairman of the division. The company
said Mr. Price plans to retire in November, when he reaches
the age of 65. Most recently Mr. Downing was vice president,
operations, for Randall, a Cincinnati maker of functional and
decorative metal and plastic parts used for automobiles.
</LP>
