<LP>
   Amertek Inc. said it filed a proposal under Canada's
Bankruptcy Act asking its creditors to allow it to defer
payment of outstanding accounts totaling about 4.5 million
Canadian dollars (US$3.9 million).
   Amertek said it is proposing to pay about 60% of that sum
